tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_links (
    link_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    node1_id INT,
    node2_id INT,
    link_status VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (node1_id) REFERENCES quantum_nodes(node_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (node2_id) REFERENCES quantum_nodes(node_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_events (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    link_id INT,
    event_type VARCHAR(50),
    event_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (link_id) REFERENCES quantum_links(link_id)
);
